com.aevi.printing

Class PrintJobStateChangedEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aevi.printing.PrintJobStateChangedEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class PrintJobStateChangedEvent
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    Contains the data associated with the state changed of a print job. This class is received by listeners after registering for print job updates on the print service.
